  "body": "### Desired Outcome\n- Propose a reputation scoring system to the team, incorporate feedback, and implement the reputation scoring system\n- After implementing the scoring system, compare the snapsync completion time to the baseline metric captured in #3853. \n- Measure how much of a positive or negative improvements we have made after the change in the scoring system \n- We'd like to optimize the scoring system for post-merge where PoS kicks in not the current PoW \n\n### Behaviors we want to reward\n- Fast response\n- Completeness of data\n- Delivers lots of data (high throughput)\n\n### Behaviors we want to punish\n- Peer takes very long time to deliver data or times out \n- Peer sends same data repeatedly\n- Peer does not have data that we require \n\n### Note\n- Mark this as an experimental feature \n\n",
